---
layout: base
permalink: /index.html
title: "Tech adventures"
description: "I am Nilushan Silva, A full stack developer from Logan, Queensland, Australia"
---

<div class="wrapper">
  <header class="full | section" style="--spot-color: var(--color-primary)">
    <div class="section__inner flow region">
      <h1 class="text-center" style="color: var(--color-light)">{{ title }}</h1>
    </div>

    {% svg "divider/waves", null, "seperator" %}
  </header>

  <article class="full | region">
    <div class="wrapper flow prose">
      
      <p>
        I am a full stack and cloud developer as a profession. This site will contain details about my technical adventures. I like to learn and practice software development during my off from work time as well. 
      </p>

      <p>
        I will be having a blog, a knowledge base through this space. 
      </p>
      
    </div>
  </article>
    
  <section class="full | region">
    <div class="wrapper flow prose">
      <h2>{{ blog.title }}</h2>
      <!-- blog intro text is optional. -->

      {% if blog.intro %}
      <p>{{ blog.intro }}</p>
      {% endif %}

      <div class="feature | region region-space-l">
        <custom-masonry layout="50-50">
          <!-- loop posts -->
          {% set itemList = collections.posts %} {% asyncEach item in
          itemList.slice(0, 4) %} {% set definedDate = item.date %} {% include
          "partials/card-blog.njk" %} {% endeach %}
        </custom-masonry>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
